data.description: This home has just enough it's the perfect size on a large 1-acre lot with room for expansion. It is also located in one of the best school districts around. You will benefit from not one, but two nice size living areas. If you want to enjoy some fresh air there is a deck attached to the back of the home perfect for hosting a BBQ or any other outdoor function. The property has a fully paved 4-car carport with additional covered parking attached to the 20x20 shop. The shop building is insulated with concrete floors, HVAC, and electricity. This shop building can accommodate various types of projects. The plumbing was replaced in 2022 and a new propane line was installed in the same year, both with transferable warranties.
